===Adjective===
'''warm'''

#a [[temperature]] slightly higher than usual, still pleasant. [[Mild|mild]] temperature: ''The tea is still warm.''
#something that causes warmth, or the impression thereof: ''This is a very warm room.''
#[[care|caring]], of relation to another person. 
#:''(we have a warm friendship)
# [[ardent]], [[zealous]] (18th century meaning)

